<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/registerQR.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>E-Authentication</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="text-box">
            <p><b>NOTE:</b> For perfoming <b>QR</b> Authentication,
                an Authenticator App is required to be setup since it will be responsible
                for scanning QR when registering for the first time and will provide the code for login once account has
                been setup on the app.
                Any Authenticator App such as Microsoft Authenticator,
                Google Authenticator, etc, can be used for scanning the QR.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="input-box">
                <header>
                    <h2>Verification</h2>
                </header>
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="<%= urlData %>">
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p>Scan the <b>QR</b> code using <b>Authenticator
                            App </b> <br>
                        and enter the generated code below.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <form class="form-box" action="/verifyQR" method="post">
                    <input type="text" name="token" autocomplete="off">
                    <div class="button">
                        <button class="submit">Submit</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>